Is that you Victoria Beckham? Designer turns heads in bold yellow dress and trench

2016-06-24

GETTY

The fashion designer swapped her usual dark and monochrome attire for something the complete opposite as she ran errands solo.

Wearing her new shorter tresses down and keeping her sunglasses firmly on, the 42-year-old wowed in an all-yellow outfit.

Victoria complemented her sun-kissed skin in a silky lemon dress, complete with ruched detailing along the front, and a coordinated trench coat.

The former Spice Girl oozed glamour as she strutted along the street after polishing off her attire with nude heels.

