During her outing, Victoria gushed about her BFF Eva Longoria with her 11.3 million Instagram followers.

"@EvaLongoria, I couldnâ€™t be more inspired by you. When women support each other, we accomplish amazing things. Celebrate the women who #LeanInTogether with you."

The mother-of-four's post comes after she spoke out following the EU Referendum's Vote Leave organisation trying to link her to their campaign.

